visibility: SANDBOX
license: OFL
category: display
subsets: menu,latin

family: Port Lligat Sans

designer: Tipo

approved: true
description: <p>Port Lligat Sans is a display typeface. \
  It has a soft variation on strokes, vertical stress, \
  and a well balance groovy rhythm. It is particularly \
  useful for both short text and headlines, but it is \
  also comfortable for reading on screen. It is designed \
  to become a super family with styles in many different \
  typographical categories. The first releases, the \
  regular Roman styles of the Sans and Slab families, \
  have the same visual weight and width. The space is \
  visually balanced for each style. As a result they \
  can be used together in many different ways.</p>

font.PortLligatSans-Regular.ttf.style: normal
font.PortLligatSans-Regular.ttf.weight: 400

